title: G5 In need of coach! sup/adc
body:
Hi im jayden my in game name is Jayden Kun. I do not expect to play for this. Sorry for all you lol boosters. But im looking for someone i can duo with in the botlane just to give me some feedback and to see how im going as a player . The rest will be worked out in game so add me for questions.

Ii look forward to hearing at least 1 reply :)
